SELECT
    ws.id AS wall_setting_id,
    a.id AS account_id,
    m.id AS media_id,
    z.id AS zone_id,
    w.id AS wall_id,
    z.is_test AS is_test,
    ws.minimum_user_reward AS minimum_user_reward,
    ws.filter_platform_type AS filter_platform_type,
    ws.ad_course_count_selection AS ad_course_count_selection,
    ws.is_deny_app_ad AS is_deny_app_ad,
    ws.accept_tag_names AS accept_tag_names,
    ws.reject_tag_names AS reject_tag_names,
    z.publish_country AS publish_country
FROM
    smaad_main.account AS a
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.media AS m ON a.id = m.account_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.zone AS z ON m.id = z.media_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.wall AS w ON z.id = w.zone_id
LEFT JOIN
    offerwall_production.wall_settings AS ws ON ws.wall_id = w.id
WHERE
    z.id = 123332994;

SELECT
    a.id AS ad_id,
    (c.`status` 
    AND d.`status` 
    AND a.`status`        
    AND (CASE 
        WHEN (d.multi_course = 1 
        AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) > 1) 
        OR (d.multi_course = 0 
        AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) = 1) THEN 1                  
        ELSE 0 
    END)        
    AND MAX((NOW() > dt.start_date 
    AND (dt.end_date IS NULL 
    OR dt.end_date > NOW())))        
    AND d.allow_pointuser = 1        
    AND FIND_IN_SET('3', GROUP_CONCAT(da.zone_type_id))       
    AND (
        SUM(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL, 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL, 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') 
                   NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0)) 
            = COUNT(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') 
                      NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL OR DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0)) 
            = COUNT(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL OR DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL OR b.hourly_stop <= NOW(), 1, 0)) 
            = COUNT(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL OR b.hourly_stop <= NOW(), 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL, 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL, 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') 
                   NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0)) 
            = COUNT(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') 
                      NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL OR DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) 
                   != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0)) 
            = COUNT(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL OR DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) 
                      != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0))        
    )) AS ad_status,
	cre.ad_size_id,
    d.id AS distribution_id,
    d.name AS distribution_name,
    pi.platform AS platform,
    COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) AS course_count,
    (CASE WHEN d.multi_course = 0 THEN b.course_name ELSE NULL END) as course_name,
    p.price,
    cre.image_url AS image_url,
    cre.video_name AS video_url,
    d.multi_course AS multi_course,
    GROUP_CONCAT((CASE 
        WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay)              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 1 THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 2 THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 3 THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
    END) ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR '(,)') AS points,
    SUM(CASE 
        WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay)              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 1 THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 2 THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 3 THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
    END) AS point,
    a.modified,
    GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time,
    GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time_unit ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time_unit,
    pt.tag_ids AS tag_ids,
    dt.start_date AS dis_term_start
FROM
    smaad_main.account ac        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.product p ON ac.id = p.account_id AND p.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.currency_rate cr ON ac.currency_id = cr.currency_id 
        AND cr.target_month = (
            SELECT MAX(cr2.target_month) 
            FROM smaad_main.currency_rate cr2
            WHERE cr2.currency_id = ac.currency_id 
            AND cr2.target_month < NOW()
        )        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.product_info pi ON p.id = pi.product_id
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.campaign c ON p.id = c.product_id AND c.campaign_type = 0 AND c.deleted IS NULL AND c.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution d ON c.id = d.campaign_id AND pi.platform = d.platform AND d.deleted IS NULL   
        AND d.allow_pointuser = 1 AND d.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution_allow_zone_type da ON d.id = da.distribution_id AND da.zone_type_id = 3        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.budget b ON d.id = b.distribution_id AND b.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT ad.id, ad.distribution_id, ad.creative_id, ad.status, ad.is_own_ad, ad.modified, ad.deleted
        FROM smaad_main.ad
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.creative AS cre ON ad.creative_id = cre.id AND cre.active = 1 AND cre.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution AS d ON d.id = ad.distribution_id AND d.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.campaign AS c ON c.id = d.campaign_id AND c.campaign_type = 0 AND c.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.product AS p ON p.id = c.product_id AND p.deleted IS NULL
        WHERE ad.deleted IS NULL AND ad.creative_id IS NOT NULL
        UNION
        SELECT va.id, va.distribution_id, va.creative_id, va.status, va.is_own_ad, va.modified, va.deleted
        FROM smaad_main.video_ad AS va
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.creative AS cre ON va.creative_id = cre.id AND cre.active = 1 AND cre.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution AS d ON d.id = va.distribution_id AND d.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.campaign AS c ON c.id = d.campaign_id AND c.campaign_type = 0 AND c.deleted IS NULL
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.product AS p ON p.id = c.product_id AND p.deleted IS NULL
        WHERE va.deleted IS NULL AND va.creative_id IS NOT NULL        
    ) a ON d.id = a.distribution_id AND a.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.creative cre ON a.creative_id = cre.id AND cre.active = 1 AND cre.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution_term dt ON d.id = dt.distribution_id AND NOW() > dt.start_date 
        AND (dt.end_date IS NULL OR dt.end_date > NOW())
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(ml.id SEPARATOR ',') AS label_ids            
        FROM smaad_main.media_label AS mdl
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.m_label AS ml ON mdl.media_id = 9 AND mdl.label_id = ml.id
    ) AS ml        
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.m_cv_place mcp ON d.cv_place_id = mcp.id
    LEFT JOIN smaad_main.pay_per_media AS pp ON d.id = pp.distribution_id 
        AND b.course_id = pp.course_id AND pp.media_id = 9        
    LEFT JOIN smaad_main.own_ad AS oa ON a.id = oa.ad_id
    LEFT JOIN smaad_main.media_linkage AS mlink ON mlink.zone_id = 9        
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT product_id, GROUP_CONCAT(pt.tag_id) as tag_ids            
        FROM smaad_main.product_tag pt
            INNER JOIN smaad_main.tag_master tm ON tm.id = pt.tag_id
        GROUP BY product_id
    ) pt ON pt.product_id = p.id
WHERE
    (c.limit_count_stop IS NULL)
    AND (c.limit_stop IS NULL)
    AND (c.monthly_stop IS NULL 
         OR DATE_FORMAT(c.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'))
    AND (c.limit_monthly_count_stop IS NULL 
         OR DATE_FORMAT(c.limit_monthly_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'))
    AND (c.daily_stop IS NULL 
         OR DATE(c.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))
    AND (c.limit_daily_count_stop IS NULL 
         OR DATE(c.limit_daily_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))
    AND (d.publish_country = 'JP')
    AND (a.is_own_ad = 0 
         OR (a.is_own_ad = 1 AND oa.account_id = 684039957))
    AND d.test_date IS NOT NULL
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT * 
        FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_black black          
        WHERE smaad_main.black.distribution_id = d.id AND black.media_id = 641991699        
    )
    AND (EXISTS (
            SELECT * 
            FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_white AS white            
            WHERE smaad_main.white.distribution_id = d.id AND white.media_id = 641991699          
        )          
        OR (NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT * 
                FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_black AS l_black              
                WHERE smaad_main.l_black.distribution_id = d.id AND FIND_IN_SET(l_black.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
            ) 
            AND EXISTS (
                SELECT * 
                FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_white AS l_white              
                WHERE smaad_main.l_white.distribution_id = d.id AND FIND_IN_SET(l_white.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
            )
        )
    )
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT id 
        FROM smaad_main.deny_ad_zone_rel AS daz          
        WHERE daz.zone_id = 641991699 AND daz.creative_id = cre.id        
    )
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT id 
        FROM smaad_main.deny_category_zone_rel AS dcz          
        WHERE dcz.zone_id = 641991699 AND dcz.category_id = p.category_id        
    )
    AND ((pi.platform = 'web' 
          AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT id 
            FROM smaad_main.deny_url_zone_rel AS duz              
            WHERE duz.zone_id = 641991699 AND pi.uri LIKE CONCAT(duz.url, '%')            
          )
         ) 
         OR ((pi.platform = 'ios' OR pi.platform = 'android') 
             AND NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT id 
                FROM smaad_main.deny_app_zone_rel AS dapz              
                WHERE dapz.zone_id = 641991699 AND dapz.app_id = pi.app_id            
             )
         )
    )  
GROUP BY
    pi.id, a.id, cre.ad_size_id  
HAVING
    ((d.multi_course = 0 AND course_count = 1) OR d.multi_course = 1)      
    AND `point` > 0      
    AND `ad_status` = 1 
    AND `point` >= 1  
ORDER BY
    cv_place_id, a.modified DESC, a.id DESC 
LIMIT 2147483647 OFFSET 0;

SELECT
    d.id as distribution_id,
    d.`name` AS distribution_name,
    d.platform AS platform,
    SUM(imp) AS imp,
    SUM(click) AS click,
    COALESCE(SUM(TRUNCATE(ordered_pay * a_cr.ttm / m_cr.ttm, m_currency.decimal_point)), 0) AS total_pay
FROM
    smaad_main.base_report
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.ad ON  smaad_main.base_report.ad_id = ad.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution d ON ad.distribution_id = d.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.campaign ON d.campaign_id = campaign.id
    AND campaign.campaign_type IN (0, 1, 3)
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.product ON smaad_main.campaign.product_id = product.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account a_ac ON smaad_main.product.account_id = a_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.zone FORCE INDEX (media_id) ON smaad_main.base_report.zone_id = zone.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.media FORCE INDEX (account_id) ON smaad_main.zone.media_id = media.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account m_ac FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON smaad_main.media.account_id = m_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_timezone tz ON m_ac.timezone_id = tz.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_currency ON m_ac.currency_id = m_currency.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.base_report_2_currency_rate br2cr FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON smaad_main.base_report.id = br2cr.base_report_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate a_cr ON br2cr.ad_currency_rate_id = a_cr.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate m_cr ON br2cr.md_currency_rate_id = m_cr.id
WHERE
     smaad_main.base_report.deleted IS NULL
    AND smaad_main.media.account_id = 684039957
    AND '2024-11-01 09:00:00' <= (base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR)
    AND (base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR) <= '2024-11-08 09:00:00'
GROUP BY
    d.id
ORDER BY
    distribution_name ASC;

    z.publish_country,
    z.pv,
    z.top_pv,
    z.uu,
    z.target_date 
FROM
    offerwall_production.zone_reports z 
WHERE
    (
        z.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW() - INTERVAL 2 HOUR, '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR) 
        AND z.updated_at <= DATE_FORMAT(NOW() - INTERVAL 2 HOUR, '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00')
    ) 
UNION
(
    SELECT
        z.id,
        z.zone_id,
        z.zone_name,
        z.publish_country,
        z.pv,
        z.top_pv,
        z.uu,
        z.target_date 
    FROM
        offerwall_production.zone_reports z 
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.block_reports b 
            ON z.id = b.zone_report_id 
    WHERE
        b.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW() - INTERVAL 2 HOUR, '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR) 
        AND b.updated_at <= DATE_FORMAT(NOW() - INTERVAL 2 HOUR, '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00')
) 
UNION
(
    SELECT
        z.id,
        z.zone_id,
        z.zone_name,
        z.publish_country,
        z.pv,
        z.top_pv,
        z.uu,
        z.target_date 
    FROM
        offerwall_production.zone_reports z 
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.block_reports b 
            ON z.id = b.zone_report_id 
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.distribution_reports d 
            ON b.id = d.block_report_id 
    WHERE
        d.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW() - INTERVAL 2 HOUR, '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR)

        a.id AS ad_id,
        (c.`status` 
        AND d.`status`

        AND (CASE 
            WHEN (d.multi_course = 1

            OR                       (d.multi_course = 0 
            AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) = 1) THEN 1                  
            ELSE 0 
        END)        
        AND MAX((NOW() > dt.start_date 
        AND (dt.end_date IS NULL

        AND d.allow_pointuser = 1        
        AND FIND_IN_SET('3',
        GROUP_CONCAT(da.zone_type_id))       
        AND (            SUM(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL,
        1,

        1,

        AND SUM(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,

        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),

        AND SUM(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))      )) AS `status`,
        cre.ad_size_id,
        d.id AS distribution_id,
        d.name AS distribution_name,
        pi.platform AS platform,
        COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) AS course_count,
        (CASE 
            WHEN d.multi_course = 0 THEN b.course_name 
            ELSE NULL 
        END) as course_name,
        p.price,
        cre.image_url AS image_url,
        cre.video_name AS video_url,
        d.multi_course AS multi_course,
        GROUP_CONCAT((CASE 
            WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL              THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay)              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 1              THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 2              THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id)  = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 3              THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        END      ) 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR '(,)') AS points,
        SUM(CASE 
            WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL              THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay)              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 1              THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 2              THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id)  = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 3              THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        END      ) AS point,
        a.modified      ,
        GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time,
        GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time_unit 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time_unit      ,
        pt.tag_ids AS tag_ids,
        dt.start_date AS dis_term_start  
    FROM
        smaad_main.account ac        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product p 
            ON ac.id = p.account_id 
            AND p.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.currency_rate cr 
            ON ac.currency_id = cr.currency_id           
            AND cr.target_month = (
                SELECT
                    MAX(target_month) 
            FROM
                smaad_main.currency_rate 
            WHERE
                currency_id = ac.currency_id 
                AND target_month < NOW()
        )        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product_info pi 
            ON p.id = pi.product_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.campaign c 
            ON p.id = c.product_id 
            AND c.campaign_type = 0 
            AND c.deleted IS NULL 
            AND c.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution d 
            ON c.id = d.campaign_id          
            AND pi.platform = d.platform 
            AND d.deleted IS NULL   
            AND d.allow_pointuser = 1          
            AND d.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_allow_zone_type da 
            ON d.id = da.distribution_id          
            AND da.zone_type_id = 3        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.budget b 
            ON d.id = b.distribution_id 
            AND b.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                ad.id,
                ad.distribution_id,
                ad.creative_id,
                ad.status,
                ad.is_own_ad,
                ad.modified,
                ad.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.ad              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON ad.creative_id = cre.id 
                    AND cre.active = 1 
                    AND cre.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = ad.distribution_id 
                    AND d.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0 
                    AND c.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id 
                    AND p.deleted IS NULL              
            WHERE
                ad.deleted IS NULL 
                AND ad.creative_id IS NOT NULL              
            UNION
            SELECT
                va.id,
                va.distribution_id,
                va.creative_id,
                va.status,
                va.is_own_ad,
                va.modified,
                va.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.video_ad AS va              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON va.creative_id = cre.id 
                    AND cre.active = 1 
                    AND cre.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = va.distribution_id 
                    AND d.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0 
                    AND c.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id 
                    AND p.deleted IS NULL              
            WHERE
                va.deleted IS NULL 
                AND va.creative_id IS NOT NULL        
        ) a 
            ON d.id = a.distribution_id 
            AND a.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.creative cre 
            ON a.creative_id = cre.id 
            AND cre.active = 1 
            AND cre.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_term dt 
            ON d.id = dt.distribution_id           
            AND NOW() > dt.start_date 
            AND (
                dt.end_date IS NULL 
                OR dt.end_date > NOW()
            )        
    INNER JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                GROUP_CONCAT(ml.id SEPARATOR ',') AS label_ids            
            FROM
                smaad_main.media_label AS mdl            
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.m_label AS ml 
                    ON mdl.media_id = 641991699 
                    AND mdl.label_id = ml.id        
            ) AS ml        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.m_cv_place mcp 
            ON d.cv_place_id = mcp.id        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.pay_per_media AS pp  
            ON d.id = pp.distribution_id 
            AND b.course_id = pp.course_id 
            AND pp.media_id = 641991699        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.own_ad AS oa         
            ON a.id = oa.ad_id        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.media_linkage AS mlink 
            ON mlink.zone_id = 123332994        
    LEFT JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                product_id,
                GROUP_CONCAT(pt.tag_id) as tag_ids            
            FROM
                smaad_main.product_tag pt            
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.tag_master tm            
                    ON tm.id = pt.tag_id            
            GROUP BY
                product_id        
        ) pt 
            ON pt.product_id = p.id  
    WHERE
        (
            c.limit_count_stop IS NULL
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_stop IS NULL
        )        
        AND (
            c.monthly_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE_FORMAT(c.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m')
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_monthly_count_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE_FORMAT(c.limit_monthly_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m')
        )        
        AND (
            c.daily_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE(c.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR)
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_daily_count_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE(c.limit_daily_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR)
        )        
        AND (
            d.publish_country = 'JP'
        )        
        AND (
            a.is_own_ad = 0 
            OR (
                a.is_own_ad = 1 
                AND oa.account_id = 684039957
            )
        )        
        AND d.test_date IS NOT NULL        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                * 
            FROM
                smaad_main.distribution_media_link_black black          
            WHERE
                black.distribution_id = d.id 
                AND black.media_id = 641991699        
        )        
        AND (
            EXISTS (
                SELECT
                    * 
                FROM
                    smaad_main.distribution_media_link_white AS white            
                WHERE
                    white.distribution_id = d.id 
                    AND white.media_id = 641991699          
            )          
            OR (
                NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        * 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_black AS l_black              
                    WHERE
                        l_black.distribution_id = d.id 
                        AND FIND_IN_SET(l_black.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
                ) 
                AND EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        * 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_white AS l_white              
                    WHERE
                        l_white.distribution_id = d.id 
                        AND FIND_IN_SET(l_white.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
                )          
            )        
        )        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                id 
            FROM
                smaad_main.deny_ad_zone_rel AS daz          
            WHERE
                daz.zone_id = 123332994 
                AND daz.creative_id = cre.id        
        )        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                id 
            FROM
                smaad_main.deny_category_zone_rel AS dcz          
            WHERE
                dcz.zone_id = 123332994 
                AND dcz.category_id = p.category_id        
        )        
        AND (
            (
                pi.platform = 'web' 
                AND            NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        id 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.deny_url_zone_rel AS duz              
                    WHERE
                        duz.zone_id = 123332994 
                        AND pi.uri LIKE CONCAT(duz.url, '%')            
                )          
            ) 
            OR (
                (
                    pi.platform = 'ios' 
                    OR pi.platform = 'android'
                ) 
                AND            NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        id 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.deny_app_zone_rel AS dapz              
                    WHERE
                        dapz.zone_id = 123332994 
                        AND dapz.app_id = pi.app_id            
                )          
            )        
        )  
    GROUP BY
        pi.id,
        a.id,
        cre.ad_size_id  
    HAVING
        (
            (
                d.multi_course = 0 
                AND course_count = 1
            ) 
            OR d.multi_course = 1
        )      
        AND `point` > 0      
        AND `status` = 1 
        AND `point` >= 1  
    ORDER BY
        cv_place_id,
        a.modified DESC,
        a.id DESC LIMIT 2147483647 OFFSET 0

SELECT

FROM
    offerwall_production.recommends AS r   
LEFT JOIN
    offerwall_production.recommend_templates AS rt 
    ON r.id = rt.recommend_id   
WHERE
    (
        rt.template_id = 51 
        OR r.template_select_type = 'all' 
    )       
    AND r.contentable_type = 'ContentSlider'       
    AND r.publish_country = 'JP'       
    AND (
        r.ad_id NOT IN (
            725872009, 800563287, 956027147, 418557813, 463683307, 
            201152675, 450283990, 617147493, 164724663, 308965857, 
            719773778, 594605452
        ) 
        OR r.ad_id IS NULL
    )       
    AND r.deleted = 0       
    AND (
        (
            r.start_at IS NULL 
            AND r.end_at IS NULL
        )           
        OR (
            r.start_at IS NULL 
            AND r.end_at >= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()
        )           
        OR (
            r.start_at <= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() 
            AND r.end_at IS NULL
        )           
        OR (
            CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() BETWEEN r.start_at AND r.end_at
        )       
    )   
GROUP BY
    ad_id,
    ad_size_id,
    linkable_type,
    linkable_id,

SELECT
    d.id AS distribution_id,
    d.`name` AS distribution_name,
    d.platform AS platform,
    SUM(imp) AS imp,
    SUM(click) AS click,
    COALESCE(
        SUM(TRUNCATE(ordered_pay * a_cr.ttm / m_cr.ttm, m_currency.decimal_point)),
        0
    ) AS total_pay
FROM
    smaad_main.base_report
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.ad ON base_report.ad_id = ad.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution d ON ad.distribution_id = d.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.campaign ON d.campaign_id = campaign.id 
    AND campaign.campaign_type IN (0, 1, 3)
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.product ON campaign.product_id = product.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account a_ac ON product.account_id = a_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.zone FORCE INDEX (media_id) ON base_report.zone_id = zone.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.media FORCE INDEX (account_id) ON zone.media_id = media.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account m_ac FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON media.account_id = m_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_timezone tz ON m_ac.timezone_id = tz.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_currency ON m_ac.currency_id = m_currency.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.base_report_2_currency_rate br2cr FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON base_report.id = br2cr.base_report_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate a_cr ON br2cr.ad_currency_rate_id = a_cr.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate m_cr ON br2cr.md_currency_rate_id = m_cr.id
WHERE
    base_report.deleted IS NULL
    AND media.account_id = 684039957
    AND ('2024-11-01 09:00:00' <= (base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR))
    AND ((base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR) <= '2024-11-08 09:00:00')
GROUP BY
    d.id
ORDER BY
    distribution_name ASC;

SELECT
    base_report.ad_id AS ad_id,
    SUM(base_report.approved_of_ordered) AS approved_of_ordered,
    SUM(base_report.total_pay) AS total_pay,
    CASE 
        WHEN SUM(base_report.ordered_cv) > 0 THEN SUM(base_report.approved_of_ordered) / SUM(base_report.ordered_cv) 
        ELSE 0 
    END AS approval_rate  
FROM
    smaad_main.base_report      
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.ad ON base_report.ad_id = ad.id      
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.zone ON base_report.zone_id = zone.id      
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.media ON zone.media_id = media.id      
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account m_ac ON media.account_id = m_ac.id      
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_timezone tz ON m_ac.timezone_id = tz.id  
WHERE
    base_report.deleted IS NULL      
    AND media.account_id = 684039957      
    AND base_report.zone_id = 123332994      
    AND (
        base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR
    ) BETWEEN '2024-10-09 18:17:13' AND '2024-11-08 18:17:13'  
GROUP BY
    base_report.ad_id  
ORDER BY
    base_report.ad_id;

    z.id AS zone_id,

    w.wall_title AS wall_title,
    CONCAT(ROUND(ml.pay_ratio, 1), '%') AS pay_ratio,

SELECT
        a.id AS ad_id,
        (c.`status` 
        AND d.`status` 
        AND a.`status`        
        AND (CASE 
            WHEN (d.multi_course = 1 
            AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) > 1) 
            OR                       (d.multi_course = 0 
            AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) = 1) THEN 1                  
            ELSE 0 
        END)        
        AND MAX((NOW() > dt.start_date 
        AND (dt.end_date IS NULL 
        OR dt.end_date > NOW())))        
        AND d.allow_pointuser = 1        
        AND FIND_IN_SET('3',
        GROUP_CONCAT(da.zone_type_id))       
        AND (            SUM(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))      )) AS `status`,
        cre.ad_size_id,
        d.id AS distribution_id,
        d.name AS distribution_name,
        pi.platform AS platform,
        COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) AS course_count,
        (CASE 
            WHEN d.multi_course = 0 THEN b.course_name 
            ELSE NULL 
        END) as course_name,
        p.price,
        cre.image_url AS image_url,
        cre.video_name AS video_url,
        d.multi_course AS multi_course,
        GROUP_CONCAT((CASE 
            WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL              THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay)              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 1              THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 2              THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id)  = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 3              THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        END      ) 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR '(,)') AS points,
        SUM(CASE 
            WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL              THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay)              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 1              THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 2              THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id)  = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            WHEN mlink.round_type = 3              THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
            ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id,
            b.course_id) = 0,
            pp.pay,
            b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))              
        END      ) AS point,
        a.modified      ,
        GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time,
        GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time_unit 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time_unit      ,
        pt.tag_ids AS tag_ids,
        dt.start_date AS dis_term_start  
    FROM
        smaad_main.account ac        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product p 
            ON ac.id = p.account_id 
            AND p.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.currency_rate cr 
            ON ac.currency_id = cr.currency_id           
            AND cr.target_month = (
                SELECT
                    MAX(target_month) 
            FROM
                smaad_main.currency_rate 
            WHERE
                currency_id = ac.currency_id 
                AND target_month < NOW()
        )        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product_info pi 
            ON p.id = pi.product_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.campaign c 
            ON p.id = c.product_id 
            AND c.campaign_type = 0 
            AND c.deleted IS NULL 
            AND c.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution d 
            ON c.id = d.campaign_id          
            AND pi.platform = d.platform 
            AND d.deleted IS NULL   
            AND d.allow_pointuser = 1          
            AND d.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_allow_zone_type da 
            ON d.id = da.distribution_id          
            AND da.zone_type_id = 3        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.budget b 
            ON d.id = b.distribution_id 
            AND b.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                ad.id,
                ad.distribution_id,
                ad.creative_id,
                ad.status,
                ad.is_own_ad,
                ad.modified,
                ad.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.ad              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON ad.creative_id = cre.id 
                    AND cre.active = 1 
                    AND cre.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = ad.distribution_id 
                    AND d.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0 
                    AND c.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id 
                    AND p.deleted IS NULL              
            WHERE
                ad.deleted IS NULL 
                AND ad.creative_id IS NOT NULL              
            UNION
            SELECT
                va.id,
                va.distribution_id,
                va.creative_id,
                va.status,
                va.is_own_ad,
                va.modified,
                va.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.video_ad AS va              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON va.creative_id = cre.id 
                    AND cre.active = 1 
                    AND cre.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = va.distribution_id 
                    AND d.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0 
                    AND c.deleted IS NULL              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id 
                    AND p.deleted IS NULL              
            WHERE
                va.deleted IS NULL 
                AND va.creative_id IS NOT NULL        
        ) a 
            ON d.id = a.distribution_id 
            AND a.`status` = 1        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.creative cre 
            ON a.creative_id = cre.id 
            AND cre.active = 1 
            AND cre.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_term dt 
            ON d.id = dt.distribution_id           
            AND NOW() > dt.start_date 
            AND (
                dt.end_date IS NULL 
                OR dt.end_date > NOW()
            )        
    INNER JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                GROUP_CONCAT(ml.id SEPARATOR ',') AS label_ids            
            FROM
                smaad_main.media_label AS mdl            
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.m_label AS ml 
                    ON mdl.media_id = 641991699 
                    AND mdl.label_id = ml.id        
            ) AS ml        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.m_cv_place mcp 
            ON d.cv_place_id = mcp.id        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.pay_per_media AS pp  
            ON d.id = pp.distribution_id 
            AND b.course_id = pp.course_id 
            AND pp.media_id = 641991699        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.own_ad AS oa         
            ON a.id = oa.ad_id        
    LEFT JOIN
        smaad_main.media_linkage AS mlink 
            ON mlink.zone_id = 123332994        
    LEFT JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                product_id,
                GROUP_CONCAT(pt.tag_id) as tag_ids            
            FROM
                smaad_main.product_tag pt            
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.tag_master tm            
                    ON tm.id = pt.tag_id            
            GROUP BY
                product_id        
        ) pt 
            ON pt.product_id = p.id  
    WHERE
        (
            c.limit_count_stop IS NULL
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_stop IS NULL
        )        
        AND (
            c.monthly_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE_FORMAT(c.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m')
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_monthly_count_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE_FORMAT(c.limit_monthly_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m')
        )        
        AND (
            c.daily_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE(c.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR)
        )        
        AND (
            c.limit_daily_count_stop IS NULL 
            OR DATE(c.limit_daily_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR)
        )        
        AND (
            d.publish_country = 'JP'
        )        
        AND (
            a.is_own_ad = 0 
            OR (
                a.is_own_ad = 1 
                AND oa.account_id = 684039957
            )
        )        
        AND d.test_date IS NOT NULL        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                * 
            FROM
                smaad_main.distribution_media_link_black black          
            WHERE
                black.distribution_id = d.id 
                AND black.media_id = 641991699        
        )        
        AND (
            EXISTS (
                SELECT
                    * 
                FROM
                    smaad_main.distribution_media_link_white AS white            
                WHERE
                    white.distribution_id = d.id 
                    AND white.media_id = 641991699          
            )          
            OR (
                NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        * 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_black AS l_black              
                    WHERE
                        l_black.distribution_id = d.id 
                        AND FIND_IN_SET(l_black.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
                ) 
                AND EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        * 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_white AS l_white              
                    WHERE
                        l_white.distribution_id = d.id 
                        AND FIND_IN_SET(l_white.label_id, ml.label_ids)            
                )          
            )        
        )        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                id 
            FROM
                smaad_main.deny_ad_zone_rel AS daz          
            WHERE
                daz.zone_id = 123332994 
                AND daz.creative_id = cre.id        
        )        
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT
                id 
            FROM
                smaad_main.deny_category_zone_rel AS dcz          
            WHERE
                dcz.zone_id = 123332994 
                AND dcz.category_id = p.category_id        
        )        
        AND (
            (
                pi.platform = 'web' 
                AND            NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        id 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.deny_url_zone_rel AS duz              
                    WHERE
                        duz.zone_id = 123332994 
                        AND pi.uri LIKE CONCAT(duz.url, '%')            
                )          
            ) 
            OR (
                (
                    pi.platform = 'ios' 
                    OR pi.platform = 'android'
                ) 
                AND            NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT
                        id 
                    FROM
                        smaad_main.deny_app_zone_rel AS dapz              
                    WHERE
                        dapz.zone_id = 123332994 
                        AND dapz.app_id = pi.app_id            
                )          
            )        
        )  
    GROUP BY
        pi.id,
        a.id,
        cre.ad_size_id  
    HAVING
        (
            (
                d.multi_course = 0 
                AND course_count = 1
            ) 
            OR d.multi_course = 1
        )      
        AND `point` > 0      
        AND `status` = 1 
        AND `point` >= 1  
    ORDER BY
        cv_place_id,
        a.modified DESC,
        a.id DESC LIMIT 2147483647 OFFSET 0

SELECT
        a.id AS ad_id,
        (c.`status` 
        AND d.`status` 
        AND a.`status` 
        AND p.deleted IS NULL 
        AND c.deleted IS NULL        
        AND d.deleted IS NULL 
        AND a.deleted IS NULL 
        AND cre.deleted IS NULL 
        AND cre.active = 1        
        AND (CASE 
            WHEN (d.multi_course = 1 
            AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) > 1) 
            OR                       (d.multi_course = 0 
            AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) = 1) THEN 1                  
            ELSE 0 
        END)        
        AND MAX((NOW() > dt.start_date 
        AND (dt.end_date IS NULL 
        OR dt.end_date > NOW())))        
        AND d.allow_pointuser = 1        
        AND FIND_IN_SET('3',
        GROUP_CONCAT(da.zone_type_id))        
        AND (            SUM(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL,
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'),
        1,
        0))            
        AND SUM(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR),
        1,
        0))            
        AND (c.limit_count_stop IS NULL)            
        AND (c.limit_stop IS NULL)            
        AND (c.monthly_stop IS NULL 
        OR DATE_FORMAT(c.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'))            
        AND (c.limit_monthly_count_stop IS NULL 
        OR DATE_FORMAT(c.limit_monthly_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR,
        '%Y%m'))            
        AND (c.daily_stop IS NULL 
        OR DATE(c.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))            
        AND (c.limit_daily_count_stop IS NULL 
        OR DATE(c.limit_daily_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))      )) AS `status`,
        cre.ad_size_id,
        d.id AS distribution_id,
        d.name AS distribution_name,
        pi.platform AS platform,
        COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) AS course_count,
        (CASE 
            WHEN d.multi_course = 0 THEN b.course_name 
            ELSE NULL 
        END) as course_name,
        p.price,
        cre.image_url AS image_url,
        cre.video_name AS video_url,
        d.multi_course AS multi_course,
        GROUP_CONCAT(b.pay 
    ORDER BY
        b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR '(,)') AS points,
        SUM(b.pay) AS `point`,
        a.modified  
    FROM
        smaad_main.account ac        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product p 
            ON ac.id = p.account_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.product_info pi 
            ON p.id = pi.product_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.campaign c 
            ON p.id = c.product_id 
            AND c.campaign_type = 0        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution d 
            ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
            AND pi.platform = d.platform        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_allow_zone_type da 
            ON d.id = da.distribution_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.budget b 
            ON d.id = b.distribution_id 
            AND b.deleted IS NULL        
    INNER JOIN
        (
            SELECT
                ad.id,
                ad.distribution_id,
                ad.creative_id,
                ad.status,
                ad.is_own_ad,
                ad.modified,
                ad.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.ad              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON ad.creative_id = cre.id              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = ad.distribution_id             
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id              
            WHERE
                ad.creative_id IS NOT NULL                  
                AND ad.id IN (
                    645483170, 404083362, 739707437, 590529501, 927640875, 121014136, 571750616, 525784061, 190325161, 937697498
                )              
            UNION
            SELECT
                va.id,
                va.distribution_id,
                va.creative_id,
                va.status,
                va.is_own_ad,
                va.modified,
                va.deleted              
            FROM
                smaad_main.video_ad AS va              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.creative AS cre   
                    ON va.creative_id = cre.id              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.distribution AS d 
                    ON d.id = va.distribution_id              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.campaign AS c     
                    ON c.id = d.campaign_id 
                    AND c.campaign_type = 0              
            INNER JOIN
                smaad_main.product AS p      
                    ON p.id = c.product_id              
            WHERE
                va.creative_id IS NOT NULL                  
                AND va.id IN (
                    645483170, 404083362, 739707437, 590529501, 927640875, 121014136, 571750616, 525784061, 190325161, 937697498
                )        
        ) a 
            ON d.id = a.distribution_id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.creative cre 
            ON a.creative_id = cre.id        
    INNER JOIN
        smaad_main.distribution_term dt 
            ON d.id = dt.distribution_id  
    GROUP BY
        pi.id,
        a.id,
        cre.ad_size_id  
    ORDER BY
        cv_place_id,
        a.modified DESC,
        a.id DESC

SELECT
    a.id AS ad_id,
    (c.`status` AND d.`status` AND a.`status`
    AND (CASE 
        WHEN (d.multi_course = 1 AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) > 1) 
        OR (d.multi_course = 0 AND COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) = 1) THEN 1
        ELSE 0 
    END)
    AND MAX((NOW() > dt.start_date AND (dt.end_date IS NULL OR dt.end_date > NOW())))
    AND d.allow_pointuser = 1
    AND FIND_IN_SET('3', GROUP_CONCAT(da.zone_type_id))
    AND (SUM(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL, 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_count_stop IS NULL, 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.monthly_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.daily_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(), 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.hourly_stop IS NULL || b.hourly_stop <= NOW(), 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL, 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_total_budget_stop IS NULL, 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE_FORMAT(b.limit_monthly_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') NOT LIKE DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'), 1, 0))
    AND SUM(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0)) = COUNT(IF(b.limit_daily_budget_stop IS NULL || DATE(b.limit_daily_budget_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) != DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR), 1, 0)))) AS `status`,
    cre.ad_size_id,
    d.id AS distribution_id,
    d.name AS distribution_name,
    pi.platform AS platform,
    COUNT(DISTINCT b.course_id) AS course_count,
    (CASE 
        WHEN d.multi_course = 0 THEN b.course_name 
        ELSE NULL 
    END) as course_name,
    p.price,
    cre.image_url AS image_url,
    cre.video_name AS video_url,
    d.multi_course AS multi_course,
    GROUP_CONCAT((CASE 
        WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay)
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 1 THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 2 THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 3 THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
    END) ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR '(,)') AS points,
    SUM(CASE 
        WHEN mlink.round_type IS NULL THEN IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay)
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 1 THEN FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 2 THEN CEIL((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        WHEN mlink.round_type = 3 THEN ROUND((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
        ELSE FLOOR((IF(STRCMP(pp.course_id, b.course_id) = 0, pp.pay, b.pay) * (mlink.pay_ratio / 100) * mlink.coin_rate / mlink.yen_rate))
    END) AS point,
    a.modified,
    GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time,
    GROUP_CONCAT(b.required_time_unit ORDER BY b.course_number ASC SEPARATOR ',') AS required_time_unit,
    pt.tag_ids AS tag_ids,
    dt.start_date AS dis_term_start
FROM
    smaad_main.account ac
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.product p ON ac.id = p.account_id AND p.deleted IS NULL
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate cr ON ac.currency_id = cr.currency_id
    AND cr.target_month = (
        SELECT MAX(target_month)
        FROM smaad_main.currency_rate
        WHERE currency_id = ac.currency_id AND target_month < NOW()
    )
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.product_info pi ON p.id = pi.product_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.campaign c ON p.id = c.product_id
    AND c.campaign_type = 0
    AND c.deleted IS NULL
    AND c.`status` = 1
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution d ON c.id = d.campaign_id
    AND pi.platform = d.platform
    AND d.deleted IS NULL
    AND d.allow_pointuser = 1
    AND d.`status` = 1
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution_allow_zone_type da ON d.id = da.distribution_id
    AND da.zone_type_id = 3
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.budget b ON d.id = b.distribution_id AND b.deleted IS NULL
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT
        ad.id,
        ad.distribution_id,
        ad.creative_id,
        ad.status,
        ad.is_own_ad,
        ad.modified,
        ad.deleted
    FROM smaad_main.ad
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.creative AS cre ON ad.creative_id = cre.id
        AND cre.active = 1
        AND cre.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution AS d ON d.id = ad.distribution_id
        AND d.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.campaign AS c ON c.id = d.campaign_id
        AND c.campaign_type = 0
        AND c.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.product AS p ON p.id = c.product_id
        AND p.deleted IS NULL
    WHERE ad.deleted IS NULL
        AND ad.creative_id IS NOT NULL
    UNION
    SELECT
        va.id,
        va.distribution_id,
        va.creative_id,
        va.status,
        va.is_own_ad,
        va.modified,
        va.deleted
    FROM smaad_main.video_ad AS va
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.creative AS cre ON va.creative_id = cre.id
        AND cre.active = 1
        AND cre.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.distribution AS d ON d.id = va.distribution_id
        AND d.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.campaign AS c ON c.id = d.campaign_id
        AND c.campaign_type = 0
        AND c.deleted IS NULL
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.product AS p ON p.id = c.product_id
        AND p.deleted IS NULL
    WHERE va.deleted IS NULL
        AND va.creative_id IS NOT NULL
) a ON d.id = a.distribution_id AND a.`status` = 1
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.creative cre ON a.creative_id = cre.id
    AND cre.active = 1
    AND cre.deleted IS NULL
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution_term dt ON d.id = dt.distribution_id
    AND NOW() > dt.start_date
    AND (dt.end_date IS NULL OR dt.end_date > NOW())
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(ml.id SEPARATOR ',') AS label_ids
    FROM smaad_main.media_label AS mdl
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.m_label AS ml ON mdl.media_id = 641991699
        AND mdl.label_id = ml.id
) AS ml
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_cv_place mcp ON d.cv_place_id = mcp.id
LEFT JOIN
    smaad_main.pay_per_media AS pp ON d.id = pp.distribution_id
    AND b.course_id = pp.course_id
    AND pp.media_id = 641991699
LEFT JOIN
    smaad_main.own_ad AS oa ON a.id = oa.ad_id
LEFT JOIN
    smaad_main.media_linkage AS mlink ON mlink.zone_id = 123332994
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT
        product_id,
        GROUP_CONCAT(pt.tag_id) as tag_ids
    FROM smaad_main.product_tag pt
    INNER JOIN smaad_main.tag_master tm ON tm.id = pt.tag_id
    GROUP BY product_id
) pt ON pt.product_id = p.id
WHERE
    (c.limit_count_stop IS NULL)
    AND (c.limit_stop IS NULL)
    AND (c.monthly_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(c.monthly_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'))
    AND (c.limit_monthly_count_stop IS NULL OR DATE_FORMAT(c.limit_monthly_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m') <> DATE_FORMAT(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR, '%Y%m'))
    AND (c.daily_stop IS NULL OR DATE(c.daily_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))
    AND (c.limit_daily_count_stop IS NULL OR DATE(c.limit_daily_count_stop + INTERVAL 9 HOUR) <> DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR))
    AND (d.publish_country = 'JP')
    AND (a.is_own_ad = 0 OR (a.is_own_ad = 1 AND oa.account_id = 684039957))
    AND d.test_date IS NOT NULL
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT *
        FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_black black
        WHERE black.distribution_id = d.id
            AND black.media_id = 641991699
    )
    AND (
        EXISTS (
            SELECT *
            FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_white AS white
            WHERE white.distribution_id = d.id
                AND white.media_id = 641991699
        )
        OR (
            NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT *
                FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_black AS l_black
                WHERE l_black.distribution_id = d.id
                    AND FIND_IN_SET(l_black.label_id, ml.label_ids)
            )
            AND EXISTS (
                SELECT *
                FROM smaad_main.distribution_media_link_label_white AS l_white
                WHERE l_white.distribution_id = d.id
                    AND FIND_IN_SET(l_white.label_id, ml.label_ids)
            )
        )
    )
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT id
        FROM smaad_main.deny_ad_zone_rel AS daz
        WHERE daz.zone_id = 123332994
            AND daz.creative_id = cre.id
    )
    AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT id
        FROM smaad_main.deny_category_zone_rel AS dcz
        WHERE dcz.zone_id = 123332994
            AND dcz.category_id = p.category_id
    )
    AND (
        (
            pi.platform = 'web'
            AND NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT id
                FROM smaad_main.deny_url_zone_rel AS duz
                WHERE duz.zone_id = 123332994
                    AND pi.uri LIKE CONCAT(duz.url, '%')
            )
        )
        OR (
            (pi.platform = 'ios' OR pi.platform = 'android')
            AND NOT EXISTS (
                SELECT id
                FROM smaad_main.deny_app_zone_rel AS dapz
                WHERE dapz.zone_id = 123332994
                    AND dapz.app_id = pi.app_id
            )
        )
    )
GROUP BY
    pi.id,
    a.id,
    cre.ad_size_id
HAVING
    ((d.multi_course = 0 AND course_count = 1) OR d.multi_course = 1)
    AND `point` > 0
    AND `status` = 1
    AND `point` >= 1
ORDER BY
    cv_place_id,
    a.modified DESC,
    a.id DESC
LIMIT 2147483647 OFFSET 0;

SELECT
    d.id as distribution_id,
    d.`name` AS distribution_name,
    d.platform AS platform,
    SUM(imp) AS imp,
    SUM(click) AS click,
    COALESCE(SUM(TRUNCATE(ordered_pay * a_cr.ttm / m_cr.ttm, m_currency.decimal_point)), 0) AS total_pay
FROM
    smaad_main.base_report
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.ad ON base_report.ad_id = ad.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.distribution d ON ad.distribution_id = d.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.campaign ON d.campaign_id = campaign.id
    AND campaign.campaign_type IN (0, 1, 3)
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.product ON campaign.product_id = product.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account a_ac ON product.account_id = a_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.zone FORCE INDEX (media_id) ON base_report.zone_id = zone.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.media FORCE INDEX (account_id) ON zone.media_id = media.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.account m_ac FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON media.account_id = m_ac.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_timezone tz ON m_ac.timezone_id = tz.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.m_currency ON m_ac.currency_id = m_currency.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.base_report_2_currency_rate br2cr FORCE INDEX (PRIMARY) ON base_report.id = br2cr.base_report_id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate a_cr ON br2cr.ad_currency_rate_id = a_cr.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.currency_rate m_cr ON br2cr.md_currency_rate_id = m_cr.id
WHERE
    base_report.deleted IS NULL
    AND media.account_id = 684039957
    AND ('2024-11-01 09:00:00' <= (base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR))
    AND ((base_report.target_datetime + INTERVAL tz.time_diff HOUR) <= '2024-11-08 09:00:00')
GROUP BY
    d.id
ORDER BY
    distribution_name ASC;

SELECT
    dbr.zone_id,
    dbr.distribution_id,
    SUM(dbr.ordered_cv) AS ordered_cv,
    SUM(dbr.ordered_gross) AS ordered_gross,
    SUM(dbr.ordered_pay) AS ordered_pay,
    SUM(dbr.total_gross) AS total_gross,
    SUM(dbr.total_pay) AS total_pay
FROM
    smaad_main.daily_base_report AS dbr
WHERE
    deleted IS NULL
    AND DATE(dbr.target_date) = DATE(NOW() + INTERVAL 9 HOUR)
GROUP BY
    dbr.zone_id,
    dbr.distribution_id;

SELECT
    z.id,
    z.zone_id,
    z.zone_name,
    z.publish_country,
    z.pv,
    z.top_pv,
    z.uu,
    z.target_date
FROM
    offerwall_production.zone_reports z
WHERE
    (
        z.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR)
        AND z.updated_at <= DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00')
    )
UNION
(
    SELECT
        z.id,
        z.zone_id,
        z.zone_name,
        z.publish_country,
        z.pv,
        z.top_pv,
        z.uu,
        z.target_date
    FROM
        offerwall_production.zone_reports z
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.block_reports b ON z.id = b.zone_report_id
    WHERE
        b.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR)
        AND b.updated_at <= DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00')
)
UNION
(
    SELECT
        z.id,
        z.zone_id,
        z.zone_name,
        z.publish_country,
        z.pv,
        z.top_pv,
        z.uu,
        z.target_date
    FROM
        offerwall_production.zone_reports z
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.block_reports b ON z.id = b.zone_report_id
    JOIN
        offerwall_production.distribution_reports d ON b.id = d.block_report_id
    WHERE
        d.updated_at >= DATE_SUB(DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), INTERVAL 3 HOUR)
        AND d.updated_at <= DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00')
);

UPDATE
    offerwall_production.view_histories vh
INNER JOIN
    offerwall_production.users u ON vh.user_id = u.id
INNER JOIN
    offerwall_production.wall_settings ws ON u.wall_setting_id = ws.id
INNER JOIN
    smaad_main.wall w ON ws.wall_id = w.id
SET
    vh.contact_usable = 1
WHERE
    vh.contact_usable = 0
    AND vh.last_viewed_at BETWEEN '2024-08-03 03:31:57' AND '2024-11-11 03:31:57'
    AND w.zone_id = 100380869
    AND EXISTS (
        SELECT
            id
        FROM
            smaad_main.orders o
        WHERE
            o.`user` = u.wall_user_id
            AND o.ad_id = vh.ad_id
            AND o.zone_id = 100380869
    );
